OL,3,CNearly 2,000 knife crimes reported in
OL,4,CBristol in single year
OL,6,FNearly 2,000 knife crimes were
OL,7,Freported in Bristol last year as new
OL,8,Ffigures reveal incidents increased by
OL,9,Fmore than a quarter.
OL,11,FData by Bristol Community Safety
OL,12,FPartnership (BCSP) showed a total of
OL,13,F1,953 crimes involving knives were
OL,14,Frecorded in the city between April
OL,15,F2023 and March 2024.
OL,17,FThat is up from 1,553 the year before,
OL,18,Fwhich represents an increase of 26 per
OL,19,Fcent.
