OL,6,FIn the report, Mark Runacres,
OL,7,Fneighbourhood policing superintendent
OL,8,Ffor Avon and Somerset Police, said:
OL,9,F"During the past 12 months, the city
OL,10,Fhas witnessed the tragic loss of young
OL,11,Flives through knife crime, bringing
OL,12,Funderstandable concern and focus on
OL,13,Fhow agencies and communities are
OL,14,Fworking together.
OL,16,F"The impacts of the awful incidents in
OL,17,FIlminster Avenue and Rawnsley Park
OL,18,Fwere felt across the city and beyond.
