OL,3,CNearly 2,000 knife crimes reported in
OL,4,CBristol in single year
OL,6,F"It takes time to grieve and find a
OL,7,Fway forward for families, individuals,
OL,8,Fcommunities and the city.
OL,10,F"For those working in the BCSP, it's a
OL,11,Ftime for reflection, learning and
OL,12,Fimproving. With the bereaved families
OL,13,Fat the heart of the response to these
OL,14,Fincidents, communities have come
OL,15,Ftogether and shown compassion and
OL,16,Fstrength to support each other."
OL,18,FCompared to other major English
OL,19,Fcities, there were relatively fewer
OL,20,Fviolent crimes recorded in Bristol
OL,21,Fthan elsewhere.
